"tid":156303,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:37:13.000Z","msg":"叉燒燒肉<br />\n其實係因為大部分燒味店啲雞都麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3415e2ca95aaf3aa77186f3cf0ec51a7bf6c5350","tid":156303,"uid":55874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:40:30.000Z","msg":"叉雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解講起燒味就一定要有叉燒 叉燒係台柱黎 一定要有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ca281cc657aca83c54891eb8f5c981a875a6a3","tid":156303,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:45:27.000Z","msg":"燒肉紅腸"},{"pid":"9443ff663759096483a09ef150a2203e558b43b5","tid":156303,"uid":56544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燒肉紅腸</blockquote><br />\n我寧願你話燻蹄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw鴛鴦雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ee272d7ee48536d81ce1d4256bf75d905b0d9a","tid":156303,"uid":72847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"一定係叉叉<br />\n兩個都要肥叉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d79683174612cc0f8f79562bb4825ea8b9527ac","tid":156303,"uid":87642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:08:24.000Z","msg":"肥叉油雞首選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但有d鋪頭油雞無咁好食<br />\n所以肥叉鴨係次選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66e3269202a5a524a78170136748f59059d8a3b","tid":156303,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:14:13.000Z","msg":"叉鵝完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明雞鴨鵝最高級係鵝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 前題係當3樣都係頂級，鵝燒得唔好，味道同口感真係可以差好遠，雞呢d就算整得差個反差都唔算大"},{"pid":"f669ce795800140d808ec4b0dbb54ec4336fcb6d","tid":156303,"uid":63062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:22:59.000Z","msg":"叉油雞<br />\n<br />\n好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfce5435adef3dde7b9cb24e02983b6ab425686f","tid":156303,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就認為 燒肉油雞 多姜蓉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主一黎咁高質<br />\n<br />\n同意"},{"pid":"41af16b9d47d43d81b669c8dfaef94fe84c65264","tid":156303,"uid":4597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:27:18.000Z","msg":"半肥叉燒鴨 多色多蔥"},{"pid":"ee1bc59997d91bdce569fcd730e9a28bee707ac6","tid":156303,"uid":84216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:31:33.000Z","msg":"廋义飯加臘腸加隻咸蛋<br />\n凍檸茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n埋單應該都要6條野"},{"pid":"e74aff86e19de1103d6c4d0e15d50de24d66f3b3","tid":156303,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>燒肉紅腸</blockquote><br />\n我寧願你話燻蹄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw鴛鴦雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食燒味為左食果隻紅腸<br />\n燒肉只係配菜黎"},{"pid":"94110cab8ff59345662f96dc27c6e9a2f055af86","tid":156303,"uid":65816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T19:33:1